headline.main: Greek Fourth Quarter Economic Contraction Worse Than Thought
headline.print_headline: Greek Fourth Quarter Economic Contraction Worse Than Thought

lead_paragraph: As Greece's slow-moving bailout talks with creditors enter a second week, the statistical authority reports that the economy contracted more in the last quarter of 2016 than initially estimated.
